0)Eidi macros kai sindiasmoi

  1)eisodos = db/construct/both
  2)exodo = table/construct/both

1)Construct idi
    c sketo   (constants/binds)
    c + table (constants/binds/relations)

  macroq eidi
    macroq sketo
    macroq + relations

2)Epistrefi table (relations->table)
  (macroq
     (qc ....))  ;;qc proeretiko


  *ean exo idi relations stin mnimi se mia metabliti tote
   (macroq {:constructs [(add c1) (add c2]}

3)Epistrefi constructs(table->relations)
  (c
    (cq ...))  ;;cq proeretiko


 *bind-constucts oxi orismata metablites apo ton pinaka

4)constructs 3 eidi queries
  1)relation statheres
    (bazoun 1 line stin :d.r)

    :d.r :d.s :d.o

    *se macroq i oxi

  2)relation-binds

    ((f) {relation [x y]})

    *se macroq i oxi

  3)relations me metablites apo ton pinaka

    :d.r ?x ?y
    :d.r ?x :d.o
    :d.r :d.s ?y

    *autes mporo mono ean eimai mesa se macroq